The spell ''[[bloodspear]]'', which [[cleric]]s of [[Gruumsh]] who were initiated in their faith's secrets could cast, allowed them to temporarily turn a [[spear]], their god's favored weapon, into a ''wounding spear''.

The ''[[rapier of puncturing]]'' was a special kind of ''+2 wounding [[rapier]]'' that was often used by the [[assassin]]s of the [[Jaezred Chaulssin]], such as [[Nimor Imphraezl]].{{Cite web enhancement/City of Wyrmshadows|6-7}}

Some veteran [[Thayan gladiator]]s had their horns, claws, and other natural weapons enhanced as ''wounding'' weapons.
